title: Get Bigger! Mola : The best run game!

container.value: 101, Garimil-ro, Gwangmyeong-si, Gyeonggi-do, Republic of Korea

creator: tinysaur
descriptionHtml:
'Get Bigger! Mola' came back with the new fantastic graphics and entertaining features!


[INTRODUCTION]

Eat small, Dodge BIG !!

Make your Molamola stronger to go to bigger world.
Collect Jellyfish to unlock various characters and buddies.

Cute & scary fishes are Mola's enemies and foods at the same time.
There are many kind of fishes such as shark, dolphin, whale, sailfish, tuna, squid, orca, seabream, and even a pig!
Try avoid them, and eat them when you get bigger!
Run and Swim fast through the ocean with your Mola!
There are also many costumes for Mola!
You could be a ghost, doctor, santa, or even a ninja!

How big is your Mola?


[FEATURES]
◈ Mola, who is closest to the heaven, has came back with the new simple graphic!
◈ Mola has survived from the brutal ocean, it's time to conquer the ocean!
◈ It's not only very easy but also super hard to play such as Flappy game.
◈ Tapping screen is the only control of this game. But do not underrate it!
◈ Mola gets stronger as it dies. Don't afraid of death!
◈ Get 'Jellyfish' by playing it. You can Upgrade your Mola with it!

[TIP]
- If you 'Upgrade' Mola, your all Mola will be upgraded! Use your Jellyfish wise
- Bring your 'Buddy' to the ocean. Your Mola will get extra effect with it!
- Use 'MAP' feature to start from where you want.
- Clear 'MISSION' and 'ACHIEVEMENT' to get huge rewards!


[ENDING]
You will see ending once you finish a game.
each character has its original ending, see it for yourself!

Did you have fun? Leave your review now!
It also helps to Like & Follow our SNS pages.
Give us big warm comment!

If you found a bug or had complains, contact us (company@tinysaur.io)
